		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've always wanted to build an arcade cabinet with a PC inside to run MAME games; except have it accept coins. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif" alt=":lol:" title="Laughing" /> 
<br />
<br />Not sure if that's feasible, though. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_confused.gif" alt=":?" title="Confused" /> 
<br />
<br />And if I could get that to work, then I'd consider making some simple PC games that work as Arcade games.

		

