		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />A coin slot is just a button press like any other arcade control, all you need is a keyboard encoder. You could even make your own out of an old keyboard if you really wanted.
<br />
<br />you may find <a href="http://www.maximumpc.com/article/features/how_build_kickass_mame_arcade_cabinet_old_pc?page=0,0" class="postlink">this article</a> useful

		

