		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's too bad Sauder or Ikea doesn't sell arcade cabinet kits, although someone <a href="http://gizmodo.com/5022607/ikea-%252B-apple--mamebook-cocktail" class="postlink">jury-rigged an Ikea Ramvik</a> as a cocktail.
<br />
<br />A problem with rigging an encoder out of a USB gamepad is that you have to make absolutely sure you don't miss a coin press. Going with a keyboard encoder, as you suggested, might be superior.

		

